The Trump Administration is urging the Supreme Court to reconsider South Dakota exemption from taxes for on line retailers

Brad Parscale managesTrump’s 2020 presidential campaign, hinted that the administration may act to raise Amazon’s postal costs in a tweet late Thursday. “Once the markets figure out that a single @usps rule change will crush @amazon ’s bottom line we will see.”
